      "$value": "GT America Standard",
      "$type": "fontFamily",
      "$description": "Body, nav, labels, UI controls, everything below the headline. The signature 0.167em tracking applies across all sizes — this is the system's most distinctive typographic choice. Use 300 for body, 400 for UI/default, 500 for emphasized subheadings and nav"
    }
  },
